{"tid":2198425,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【港朝換代】護苗基金 一盤混賬 - 大灣區國舅爺","createTime":"2020-09-11T10:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T10:45:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6b3ae137a83ca46311ad69b3260045c51172d4ed","tid":2198425,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:45:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200911/D57OEMA2R5BUTFIH5OBARQA5FM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200911%2FD57OEMA2R5BUTFIH5OBARQA5FM%2F&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fklZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=7ce54bb9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200911%2FD57OEMA2R5BUTFIH5OBARQA5FM%2F&h=5296e6a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200911/D57OEMA2R5BUTFIH5OBARQA5FM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【港朝換代】護苗基金 一盤混賬 - 大灣區國舅爺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5mqLT03V1RejVIMzyFWcaT4m9Bo=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BEYZBSKCIJG43EH7MWWCHC73OY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5mqLT03V1RejVIMzyFWcaT4m9Bo%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBEYZBSKCIJG43EH7MWWCHC73OY.jpg&h=7ddafe12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■蕭芳芳與今屆政府走得很近，政務司司長張建宗上載與蕭芳芳的「碰踭」相，表示感謝對方支持全民檢測。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n慈善機構對警察濫暴視若無睹，引起香港人厭惡，更逼使外界追查背後賬目所隱含的偽善！。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n護苗基金於1998年由蕭芳芳創辦，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n錢不會說謊，護苗基金自詡「籌款效益高，大可放膽擴展服務」，但原來所謂效益，是把收入「內化」！前輩遮打道口水佬就把護苗基金的年報抽絲剝繭，發現去年從普羅大眾收取捐款約258萬元、從商家收取捐款約352萬元，卻把當中450萬元用作員工薪酬及福利，佔總捐款74%！<br />\n<br />\n護苗基金聲稱「旨在保護18歲以下人士免於遭受性侵犯」，驟看起來，護苗基金更像一個手執88牌（Section 88）、免稅燒錢搞個人品牌形象的組織，而不是把資源投放在實質個案協助，以去年為例，投放在輔導工作的支出僅得2.4萬元，只佔全年總開支0.3%。<br />\n<br />\n正如口水佬所講：「。。。。。。。」<br />\n<br />\n大灣區國舅爺"}]}